Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.90,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,…气氛并不是由装饰来营造的\N{\r原文字幕}...the atmosphere will not be painted on the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:54.10,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,- 让我举例来说-- - 这得我自己来判断\N{\r原文字幕}- Let me give you an example-- - This I had to see for myself.
