Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.00,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,运枪车被劫，有人暴跳如雷，而警察们却束手无策\N{\r原文字幕}Someone was mad about that truck hijacking and the cops had nothing.
